Description: Provides tools for Markov embedding of ranked and unlabeled evolutionary trees.
	The package extends the 'fmatrix' package; see "https://github.com/RSamyak/fmatrix/tree/main".
	It provides the necessary tools to seamlessly translate between the F-matrix and path representation presented in NAME OF PAPER HERE.
